{"tid":2393383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獲女友鞭策下體能提升洪永成 笑稱：有進步囉！","createTime":"2021-02-03T11:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T13:53:08.000Z","uid":46896,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"10d503a4e5f734e4b3df5070449353c47356c5fd","tid":2393383,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:48:53.000Z","msg":"洪永城（Tony）在宣傳新劇《陀槍師姐2021》孭起鄧佩儀時「紅都面晒」，他笑言對方望落輕磅，實則骨重，加上自己年紀不輕，又少吃補腰藥，難免有點吃力。Tony又指平時是女友梁諾妍（Inez）孭他，皆因對方是運動健將，他在女友鞭策下，體能節節上升，打算年底跟女友跑半馬拉松。笑問女友有否讚他「勁咗」？他笑說：「OK啦！有進步囉！」<br />\n<br />\n談到Inez明天生日，Tony表示已預留整天陪女友，又笑說：「連荷里活大片找我試鏡都不去呀！活動已安排了，禮物也買好。（送戒指嗎？）不是啦！總之是貼身又貼心。」"},{"pid":"e0069ea7c18efaa219d9a70b32b23bbbd6030e10","tid":2393383,"uid":33789,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"鞭策下體"},{"pid":"b04a24b66b0e08cff536df8fdfaa667278070a76","tid":2393383,"uid":238117,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:50:36.000Z","msg":"鞭策下體 重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342a44676dab0156a1d32cb5d7b9b0e442a18505","tid":2393383,"uid":72929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:50:52.000Z","msg":"兒子生性"},{"pid":"9aed56ddddffee8c43dd5499baec64a857f3d2e9","tid":2393383,"uid":135877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8a0e3774dbb1f184a6bb65e00d5d7dbc87a969","tid":2393383,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b04a24b66b0e08cff536df8fdfaa667278070a76","tid":2393383,"uid":238117,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:50:36.000Z","msg":"鞭策下體 重口味<img src=\"/assets/